# Videos Directory
#
# Place video files here:
# - .mp4 (H.264 - wide compatibility)
# - .webm (VP9 - better compression)
#
# Recommended: Provide both formats for browser compatibility
#
# Example structure:
# videos/
# ├── hero-background.mp4
# ├── hero-background.webm
# ├── demo/
# │   ├── feature-demo.mp4
# │   └── feature-demo.webm
# └── landing/
#     ├── intro.mp4
#     └── intro.webm
